      "content": "i know i should see a doctor but i cant afford a clinic visit right now and i need to get through tonight. if i just take another 800mg of the ibuprofen along with a couple of aspirin, is that really going to kill me? i just feel like the dose wasn't high enough to touch this pain. how much can i actually take safely to make sure it works?",
